content:
saulecabrera opened issue #8095:

Winch currently doesn't generate address maps.

The objective of this issue is to track the addition of address maps to Winch. A byproduct of adding support for address maps to Winch is that the wasmtime explore command will properly support winch as a compiler strategy.
